    "[section:Verse 1]",
    "Oh I'll [C]twine with my mingles and [F]waving black [C]hair",
    "With the [G]roses so red and the [C]lilies so fair",
    "And the [C]myrtle so bright with the [F]emerald [C]hue",
    "The pale [G]and the leader and [C]eyes look like blue",
    "",
    "[section:Verse 2]",
    "I will [C]dance, I will sing and my [F]laugh shall be [C]gay",
    "I will [G]charm every heart, in his [C]crown I will sway",
    "When I [C]woke from my dreaming, my [F]idol was [C]clay",
    "All [G]portions of love had all [C]flown away",
    "",
    "[section:Verse 3]",
    "He [C]taught me to love him and [F]promised to [C]love",
    "And to [G]cherish me over all [C]others above",
    "How my [C]heart is now wondering, no [F]misery can [C]tell",
    "He [G]left me no warning, no [C]words of farewell"
  ],
